<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="/output.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Uchegbu family tree home page</title>
    <style>
        html,
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-flow-row">
        <!-- Navbar -->
        <div class="bg-primary1 text-white grid lg:grid-flow-row">
            <div class="px-4 flex justify-between h-24 lg:px-10">
                <div class="flex items-center lg:grid lg:grid-flow-col">
                    <img src="/img/logo.png" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="hidden w-3/6 pl-52 lg:col-span-2 lg:grid lg:justify-center lg:items-center">
                    <ul class=" grid grid-flow-col gap-28">
                        <li class="transition hover:underline"><a href="/">Home</a></l>
                        <li class="transition hover:underline"><a href="/about">About Us</a></li>
                        {{#if isloggedIn}}
                        <li class="transition hover:underline"><a href="/edit_tree">Edit Tree</a></li>
                        <li class="transition hover:underline"><a href="/family_tree_search">View Tree</a></li>
                        {{else}}
                        <li class="transition hover:underline"><a href="/about">Learn More</a></li>
                        {{/if}}
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <img class="self-center w-8 h-8 lg:hidden" src="/img/menu1.png" alt="">
                <div class="hidden items-center lg:grid lg:grid-flow-col lg:text-xl lg:ml-0">
                    {{#if isloggedIn}}
                    <a href="/logout" onclick="confirmLogout()"
                        class="bg-white rounded-lg h-fit text-primary1 w-44 p-4 text-center shadow-lg mr-0 ml-40">Logout</a>
                    {{else}}
                    <a href="/login"
                        class="border-primary2 bg-white h-fit text-primary1 border-l-2 rounded-lg shadow-primary2 shadow-lg w-36 p-4 text-center  hover:text-white hover:bg-primary1">Login</a>
                    <a class=" text-white border-primary2 h-fit border-l-2 rounded-lg shadow-primary2 shadow-lg w-36 p-4 text-center"
                        href="/signup">Sign Up</a>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-primary2 flex h-10 items-center justify-center lg:grid lg:grid-flow-col">
                <img class="" src="/img/star.png" alt="">
                <p>Documenting generations and more to come.....</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- main page -->
        <div class="w-screen">
            <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-flow-col lg:p-28 lg:text-primary2 lg:h-64 lg:absolute lg:block ">
                <div class="hidden lg:grid">
                    <img class=" lg:w-96 lg:-ml-10 lg:rounded-sm  " src="/img/home_pic.jpg" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="p-12 pl-36">
                    <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold h-24 mt-6">About Us<img class="inline-block" src="/img/leaf.png"
                            alt=""></h1>
                    <h3 class="text-lg text-primary1 tracking-widest">THE FAMILY TREE APP</h3>
                    <p>Welcome to our family tree software! We are a passionate team of developers and genealogy
                        enthusiasts dedicated to providing a seamless and enjoyable experience for creating and
                        exploring your family history.

                        Our software is designed to empower individuals, genealogists, and families worldwide to uncover
                        their heritage, strengthen familial bonds, and preserve their unique stories. We believe that
                        everyone deserves to know and celebrate their roots, and our user-friendly platform makes it
                        easier than ever to build comprehensive family trees.

                        With our intuitive interface, you can effortlessly document and visualize your family
                        connections. Add family members, link relationships, and include important details such as
                        dates, photos, and personal stories. Dive into the past, discover intriguing connections, and
                        preserve cherished memories for future generations.

                        We understand the importance of privacy and data security when it comes to handling sensitive
                        family information. You can trust that our software employs robust security measures to
                        safeguard your data. Your family tree and personal journey remain private and secure within our
                        platform.

                        Beyond providing exceptional software, we are committed to supporting you on your genealogy
                        journey. Our dedicated customer support team is here to assist you, answer your questions, and
                        ensure that you make the most of our software's capabilities. We value your feedback and
                        continuously strive to improve our software based on user insights and industry best practices.

                        At our family tree software, we believe that your family's story is a testament to the
                        connections that shape your identity. We are honored to be a part of your journey as you unravel
                        the stories and relationships that define your unique heritage.

                        Thank you for choosing our family tree software. Start exploring your family's history today and
                        embark on a meaningful journey of discovery.
                        <br><br>
                        Sincerely,<br>
                        The Family Tree Software Team
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class=" z-10 grid grid-flow-row w-full bg-transparent text-primary2 h-64 absolute">
                <div class="grid grid-flow-row grid-rows-6">
                    <div class="border-green-700 grid grid-flow-col justify-end">
                        <div class="h-8 w-80 bg-white shadow-xl border-x-2 border-b-4"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border-blue-700">
                        <div class="z-10 h-28 w-36 opacity-60 blur-sm mx-8 bg-white shadow-2xl"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border-red-700">
                        <div class="z-10 h-20 mx-96 w-28 opacity-60 blur-sm mx-8 bg-white shadow-2xl"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border-green-700 grid grid-flow-col justify-end">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- footer -->
        <!-- <div>
            <p>Designed By: ITS.</p>
        </div> -->
    </div>
    <script>
        function confirmLogout() {
            if (confirm('Are you sure you want to log out?')) {
                window.location.href = '/logout';
            }
        }
    </script>
</body>

</html>